{
  "_comment": "Restricted seccomp allowlist for the hardened agent. Default action DENY (ENOSYS); only the syscalls needed by node/python/glibc are allowed. Dangerous syscalls (mount, ptrace, bpf, kexec, keyctl, add_key, unshare, setns, pivot_root, reboot, init_module, delete_module, swapon, etc.) are absent from the allowlist and therefore blocked. Tuned empirically against the agent image.",
